                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The sticky toffee hound is reduced to 0 hit points by any method other than its water soluble weakness</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The sticky toffee hound explodes, dealing @Damage[1d4[bludgeoning],1d4[fire]|options:area-damage] damage in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:15] with a @Check[reflex|dc:15|basic|options:area-effect] save.</p>"
