                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A sweet residue cakes the tracks left by a sticky toffee hound. A creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Track]{Tracking} the hound can roll a [[/act track skill=cooking-lore]]{Cooking Lore} or [[/act track skill=crafting]]{Crafting} check instead of a Survival check. The creature can apply any modifiers to this check that involve identifying or preparing food, such as those granted by the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Seasoned] skill feat or the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Supertaster] general feat.</p>"
                },
