                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature hit by the sticky toffee hound's headbutt Strike is splattered by the sticky toffee sauce that soaks the creature's body, becoming @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} until the end of their next turn. On a critical hit, the creature instead becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2}.</p>"
                },
